<p class="entry-meta"><time class="entry-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-01-11T00:00:13+00:00">January 11, 2019</time> <span class="entry-by">by</span> <span class="entry-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/author/lace/" class="entry-author-link" itemprop="url" rel="author"><span class="entry-author-name" itemprop="name">Lace</span></a></span> </p></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><figure id="attachment_5255" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5255" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-300x225.jpeg" alt="The 5 Best 4K Wallpaper Apps For iPhone X " width="700" height="526" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-768x577.jpeg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-1024x769.jpeg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8.jpeg 1332w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5255" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-300x225.jpeg" alt="The 5 Best 4K Wallpaper Apps For iPhone X " width="700" height="526" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-768x577.jpeg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8-1024x769.jpeg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/photo-1512499639435-ca992b59f3c8.jpeg 1332w"