<p>Design-wise the iPhone X does not look like its predecessors. Apple has definitely taken a huge leap with its innovative design.</p><div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

