<p>And since the iPhone X has a wider screen display, find out the best 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X to feature on your device.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/4k-resolution-wallpapers-for-iphone-x/">Related: Best 4k Wallpapers For iPhone X!</a></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">5 Best 4k Wallpaper Apps For iPhone X</h2>
<p>The very first thing you will notice on an iPhone is the wallpaper. And with the iPhone&#8217;s 5.8-inch OLED all-screen display, that is very hard to miss.</p><div class='code-block code-block-2' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="4728128714"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<p>With a screen that wide, for sure you will only want to feature high-resolution 4k wallpapers.</p>
<p>That is also a very nice way to customize your device and make it stand out from the rest.</p>
<p>But if you are wondering where to get high-resolution wallpapers, worry no more! There are a lot of sources that you can get wallpapers from anytime.</p><div class='code-block code-block-3' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="8531642354" data-ad-format="link" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<p>But in this article, we have got you covered. We will give you the 5 best 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X!</p>
<h3>1. Vellum Wallpapers</h3>
<figure id="attachment_5263" style="width: 450px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5263" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate-300x272.jpg" alt="Vellum Wallpapers App" width="450" height="407" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate-300x272.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate.jpg 750w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5263" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate-300x272.jpg" alt="Vellum Wallpapers App" width="450" height="407" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate-300x272.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphonxvellumupdate.jpg 750w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Vellum Wallpapers App</figcaption></figure>
<p>If you are looking on where to look for 4k wallpapers for iPhone X, <em>Vellum Wallpapers</em> will take care of that for you. It is such a sight for sore eyes and for a good reason.</p>
<p>You have a lot of options for 4k resolution wallpapers that will last you a life time. You can choose from the thousand available designs that will surely make your iPhone X stand out.</p>
<p>It has hundreds of 4k high-resolution wallpapers for all the categories you could every think of.</p>
<p>And not just that, Vellum Wallpapers also presents these wallpapers in a manner that is very pleasing to the eyes.</p>
<p>It is very well-organized that looking over hundreds wallpapers would not feel like a task.</p>
<p>Overall, <em>Vellum Wallpapers</em> is one of the best 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X there is!</p>
<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1095068317/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /></noscript></a></p>
<h3>2. WLLPPR &#8211; Background Wallpapers</h3>
<figure id="attachment_5269" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5269" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-300x103.png" alt="WLLPPR - Background Wallpapers" width="700" height="240" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-300x103.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-768x263.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-1024x351.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM.png 1470w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5269" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-300x103.png" alt="WLLPPR - Background Wallpapers" width="700" height="240" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-300x103.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-768x263.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM-1024x351.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-07-at-11.39.00-PM.png 1470w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">WLLPPR &#8211; Background Wallpapers</figcaption></figure>
<p>For someone who loves and is fascinated with the planet Earth and the universe, <em>WLLPPR</em> would be a must-have app for you.</p>
<p>It features amazing and stunning wallpapers in 4k high-definition which makes it one of the favorite 4k wallpaper apps on iPhone X.</p>
<p>With a vast selection of beautiful images of the universe, it sure does make science aficionados go wild.</p>
<p>The app also has cool features like being able to share the location of your selected wallpaper to your friends and family.</p>
<p>With <em>WLLPPR &#8211; Background Wallpapers, </em>it would surely make us in awe of the beautiful planet we live in and the universe that we are a part of.</p>
<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/id991182525/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /></noscript></a></p>
<h3>3. Live Wallpapers For Me</h3>
<figure id="attachment_5272" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5272" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-300x158.png" alt="Live Wallpapers For Me" width="700" height="368" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-300x158.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-768x403.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1024x538.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5272" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-300x158.png" alt="Live Wallpapers For Me" width="700" height="368" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-300x158.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-768x403.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1024x538.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Live Wallpapers For Me</figcaption></figure>
<p>If you are looking for the best 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X, Live Wallpapers For Me is worth the download.</p>
<p>And this app puts the <a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/how-to-use-3d-touch-on-iphone/">3D touch feature on iPhone X</a> into good use.</p>
<p>This app has tons of available live 4k wallpapers that would look so amazing on your iPhone. It is like hitting two birds with one stone.</p>
<p>Not only do you get to download 4k high-resolution wallpapers, you also get live and animated ones. So, selecting your next wallpapers would be so fun now, right?</p>
<p>Even better, the categories varies from Sci-Fi, Animals, Water, Fire, Nature and so much.</p>
<p>Now, you would not have to worry on running out of animated high-quality wallpapers for iPhone X.</p>
<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1069361548/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /></noscript></a></p>
<h3>4. Walli &#8211; Cool Wallpapers HD</h3>
<figure id="attachment_5280" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5280" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-300x205.jpg" alt="Walli - Cool Wallpapers HD" width="700" height="479" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-300x205.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-768x525.jpg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-1024x700.jpg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5280" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-300x205.jpg" alt="Walli - Cool Wallpapers HD" width="700" height="479" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-300x205.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-768x525.jpg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0-1024x700.jpg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screen-0.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Walli &#8211; Cool Wallpapers HD</figcaption></figure>
<p>If you are looking for creative and artistic wallpapers to feature on your widescreen display, look no further. <em>Walli </em>has got your back!</p>
<p><em>Walli </em>is the hub where the best artists and graphic designers share their best works. This is a community where only the best around the world contribute and share their artwork.</p>
<p>So, you can then be assured that you can get the most unique and equally beautiful artwork ever.</p>
<p>And going around is very easy as well. All artworks are divided into categories so you will not have a hard time looking for the right wallpaper.</p>
<p>Their available categories are cute, retro, superheroes, humour, movie &amp; TV shows and much more.</p>
<p>Finally, you can also follow the artists you like on their social media so you will be up to date with their latest artwork.</p>
<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1061097668/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /></noscript></a></p>
<h3>5. Everpix &#8211; Cool HD Wallpaper</h3>
<figure id="attachment_5281" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-5281" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-300x158.png" alt="Everpix - Cool HD Wallpaper" width="700" height="368" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-300x158.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-768x403.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-1024x538.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-5281" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-300x158.png" alt="Everpix - Cool HD Wallpaper" width="700" height="368" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-300x158.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-768x403.png 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1-1024x538.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1200x630wa-1.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Everpix &#8211; Cool HD Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>There are thousands of available wallpapers to choose from. And all of the wallpapers are in 4k resolution, so that is a plus.</p>
<p>You can browse 4k resolution wallpapers over multiple categories like nature, space, animals, abstract and so many others. They also have a collection of 4k live photos.</p>
<p>The app also has many useful features like the option to mark your liked wallpapers as &#8216;Favorite&#8217;. This will let you access the ones your marked as &#8216;Favorite&#8217; later.</p>
<p>You can also preview the wallpapers on your iPhone lock screen to check whether you really like it on your iPhone X.</p>
<p>Ever thinking of changing your lock screen wallpapers more than once in one day?</p>
<p>Finally, you do not have to worry on dealing outdated wallpapers as the app has new entries everyday.</p>
<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/id921160527/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-135 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Download-on-the-App-Store-e1533591028140.png" alt="" width="256" height="80" /></noscript></a></p>
<h2>Wrapping Up Things&#8230;</h2>
<p>Nowadays, if you are not using 4k high-resolution on your iPhone X lock screen then you are not doing it right.</p>
<p>It is a good way to take advantage of its widescreen OLED display.</p>
<p>The perfect wallpaper is a game-changer. Plus, it gives your device a unique identity and to really know that it is in fact your own.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m sure your device will not experience any dull moments with our list of best 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X!</p>
<p><strong>Which one from our list of 4k wallpaper apps for iPhone X do you already have? Do you know other apps with 4k resolution wallpapers? Comment down your answers below!</strong></p>
